# Cloudflare Pages redirects. Processed before static-asset matching.
# Force the canonical lowercase casing for known sections with a clean 301,
# so crawlers that discovered a mixed-case URL get a proper redirect instead
# of a client-side soft redirect to the homepage.
#
# Do NOT add a catch-all "/* /index.html 200" rule here: it would serve a 200
# HTML shell for every unknown URL (soft 404) and re-create the redirect/404
# problems in Search Console. Unmatched routes intentionally fall through to
# the static /404.html, which Cloudflare serves with a real HTTP 404.

/Angular      /angular      301
/Dotnet       /dotnet       301
/DotNet       /dotnet       301
/DOTNET       /dotnet       301
/Sql          /sql          301
/SQL          /sql          301
/Test-Me      /test-me      301
/Test-me      /test-me      301
/Dashboard    /dashboard    301
/Leaderboard  /leaderboard  301
